## Development Workflow

1.  **Start `watch-sass`:**

    * In your terminal, run: `npm run watch-sass`
    * This will watch for changes in `scss/style.scss` and automatically compile it to `css/style.css`.

2.  **Open with Live Server VS Code Extension:**

    * In VS Code, open your `index.html` file.
    * Right-click anywhere in the file and select "Open with Live Server."
    * Live Server will open your `index.html` in your browser and automatically reload when you make changes.

3.  **Develop:**

    * Edit your `index.html`, `scss/style.scss`, or other files.
    * Live Server will automatically refresh your browser, and the `watch-sass` script will automatically recompile your Sass.
